==Serbian==
===Noun===
'''друг''' ''m s'', (''pl:'' '''другови''')
# a [[male]] [[friend]]
#:''Петар је мој '''друг'''.'' (Peter is my friend.)
# A [[comrade]], especially among Partisans during World War II.
#:'''''Друг''' Прле је разнео воз.'' (Comrade Prle blew up the train.)
# Used to address people, especially during communism in Yugoslavia.
#:'''''Друже''' наставниче, када нам почиње час?'' (Comrade teacher, when will our class begin?)
